dc_title_s: L'Amerique septentrionale Dressée sur les observations de Mrs. de l'Academie Royale des Sciences & quelques autres, & sur les memoires les plus recens; par G. de L'Isle.
dc_description_s: Shows routes of explorers of the Pacific Ocean. Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridian: [Ferro]. Includes "Avertissement." 1 map hand col.; 43 x 57 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: L'Isle, Guillaume de, 1675-1726.,Schenk, Pierre.,De La Vergne, Earl W.
